    "updated_at": "2017-05-07T09:08:44Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "From what I have read in #11147 there are a couple of use cases:\r\n\r\nThis PR addresses:\r\nDouble click a single unit during\r\n- [x] Live play\r\n- [x] Replay\r\n- [x] Spectating a replay\r\n\r\nIt will correctly select units belonging to the owner of the one unit that was double clicked.\r\n\r\nSelect all actors of type hotley (w)\r\n- [ ] Live play\r\n- [ ] Replay\r\n- [ ] Spectating a replay\r\n\r\nThis is more complicated as this currently checks who is currently spectating and subsequently restricting what can be selected.\r\n\r\nAs a compounding factor, fake buildings are in the mix. #8195\r\n\r\nSome guidance in how to proceed next or squashing this PR completely would be appreciated.\r\n"
  },
