    "body": "I assume this is great feature (double click,SelectUnitsByTypeKey,SelectAllUnitsKey) for spectators so I would like that either @aydjay or I if he preferred tries to finish it, seems to be almost done.\r\n\r\n@pchote Do you agree that when spectator selects multiple units, we would support SelectUnitsByTypeKey and SelectAllUnitsKey hotkeys only when all units belong to the same player? In such case it is simple, we'll use unit.Owner instead of player like for double click.\r\n"
